sequenceDiagram
    actor Buyer
    actor Artisan
    participant API as Craftistan Spring API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL Database
    participant Gemini as Google Gemini API

    %% Artisan Interaction
    Artisan->>API: 1. Login & Get JWT Token
    API-->>Artisan: Token
    Artisan->>API: 2. Create Handicraft Product (Auth required)
    API->>DB: Save Base Product Info
    API-)Gemini: 3. Async Translate (Urdu, Punjabi, etc.)
    Gemini--)API: Return Translations
    API->>DB: Store Translated Data
    
    %% Buyer Interaction
    Buyer->>API: 4. Browse Products & Ask Chatbot
    API-->>Buyer: Localized Product Catalog
    Buyer->>API: 5. Checkout & Place Order
    API->>DB: 6. Deduct Stock & Create Order Record
    API-->>Artisan: 7. Notify Artisan of New Order
    API-->>Buyer: 8. Order Confirmation
    
    %% Fulfillment & Review
    Artisan->>API: 9. Update Order Status to 'SHIPPED'
    API->>DB: Update Status
    Buyer->>API: 10. Write 'Verified Purchase' Review
    API->>DB: Validate Purchase & Save Review
